    PrivNet([Private Network\n192.168.1.0/24])

    PrivNet --> HostA[Host A\n192.168.1.10:54321]
    PrivNet --> HostB[Host B\n192.168.1.20:54322]

    HostA --> NAT[NAT Router\nPublic IP: 203.0.113.5]
